// EXTEND PATH

// Returns a system specific path of current record base on  
// current module + subModule preceding current records primaryKey

// Function Name : jsys.extendPath
// Parameters : key
// Use example : jsys.extendPath ( key )

JSONGetElement ( $$STATE ; "currentState.path" ) & "." & key

// This is widely used to read or write record state in STATE

